Invocation Name: genoa township
des: Get the latest news and information you need to stay up-to-date with what is going on in Genoa Township, Ohio, USA. The skill provides news updates, enables the user to listen to Trustee Meeting audio, and find contact information in order to follow-up with a Trustee, Administrator or Director with questions or concerns. Ask about trash day, parks, and events for even more information about Genoa Township, Ohio.
